Description: mcmodule provides a framework for building modular Monte Carlo risk analysis models. It extends the capabilities of mc2d to facilitate working with multiple risk pathways, variates and scenarios. The package includes tools for creating stochastic objects from data frames, visualising results, and performing uncertainty, sensitivity and convergence analysis.
